law.catch_line: Taxes levied under KRS 136.1801 to 136.1806 not exclusive.
law.text: The taxes levied by KRS 136.1801 to 136.1806 are taxes on the watercraft only. The taxes levied by KRS 136.1801 to 136.1806 shall be in addition to any other taxes levied by state or local jurisdictions on any corporation.
law.history: Created 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 169, sec. 6, effective January 1, 2008.
